\theta_{kl}
\cos\theta_{kl}=\frac{1}{2}(\cos(\frac{2\pi k}{n})+\cos(\frac{2\pi l}{n}))
t
\cos(t\theta_{kl})\approx\frac{1}{2}(\cos(\frac{2\pi kt}{n})+\cos(\frac{2\pi lt}{n}))
\theta_{k\ell}
\cos(\theta_{k\ell}) = \tfrac12 \bigl( \cos(\tfrac{2\pi k}n) + \cos(\tfrac{2\pi \ell}n) \bigr)
\theta_{k\ell}
\cos\theta_{kl}=\frac{1}{2}\cos\frac{2\pi k}{n}+\frac{1}{2}\cos\frac{2\pi l}{n}
\theta_{kl}
1-\theta_{kl}^2\approx\frac{1}{2}(1-\frac{4\pi^2k^2}{n^2}+1-\frac{4\pi^2l}{n^2})=1-\frac{2\pi^2k^2+2\pi^2l^2}{n^2}
\theta_{kl}=O(\frac{k+l}{n})
